1.1.name: wordpress/facebook-like-and-send-2-in-1
1.1.description:
• Add Facebook Like and Send Button to your wordpress blog.
  • You have options to insert buttons to any posts, pages or both.
  • You have options to insert buttons after the content, before the content or both.
  • Plugin automatically include Open Graph Tags.
  • Display buttons in different languages
  • Very simple configuration.

Visit plugin site: http://www.darkomitrovic.com/wp-plugin/facebook-like-and-send-button/
